    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >赶紧系好安全带！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/bd9a753d443e64aed4f57f858def94a7.poster.avif?t=1727959454\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/bd9a753d443e64aed4f57f858def94a7.webm?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/bd9a753d443e64aed4f57f858def94a7.mp4?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>成为飞车跑酷大师！《浣熊硬探：心跳飚车党》是一款时间竞速精确平台游戏，你将飙车穿行于被水淹没的温哥华，在大楼上下左右全方位飞跃，发掘异想天开的近路，努力成为全城最快的车手！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/27b6b440ea499aface6a34944c218d35.poster.avif?t=1727959454\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/27b6b440ea499aface6a34944c218d35.webm?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/27b6b440ea499aface6a34944c218d35.mp4?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第一步：飙速烧胎</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一脚把油门踩到底，驶上绿色的加速面板，在空中呼啸飞弛！循规蹈矩依着主干道开完全程，随后你会立即发现，真正的游戏才刚刚开始！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/e191846f18005b8a35a313f84325f78e.poster.avif?t=1727959454\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/e191846f18005b8a35a313f84325f78e.webm?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/e191846f18005b8a35a313f84325f78e.mp4?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第二步：发掘近路</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >研究七拐八绕的关卡布局，摸索更快通关的方法！寻找能引领你曲径通幽的“心心”，探出自己的一套独门近路，从而称霸全球排行榜（以及力压好友一头！！！）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/380ebe982965866efa9318f3fdd3ea77.poster.avif?t=1727959454\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/380ebe982965866efa9318f3fdd3ea77.webm?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/380ebe982965866efa9318f3fdd3ea77.mp4?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第三步：屡败屡战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驾驭体内的洪荒之力！只是稍微开歪了点，就从路上掉了下去？没关系，只要优雅地大吼大叫一番，再若无其事地重新回到路上就好！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/f1d2474beac0237e112d24d984c40325.poster.avif?t=1727959454\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/f1d2474beac0237e112d24d984c40325.webm?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001200/extras/f1d2474beac0237e112d24d984c40325.mp4?t=1727959454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第四步：横冲直撞</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记住：心中无墙，则天下无墙。所以你只管向前开，撞烂多少算多少，开辟全新道路，尽情享受在满是警察的世界里制造混乱的乐趣吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >听着就爽！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4-6小时的游戏流程。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 19个九曲十八弯的关卡，关关满载着隐藏的近路、警方设下的路障以及匪夷所思的混乱。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 可重玩性超高的关卡，偏离道路、开辟巧径，不断缩短完成时间。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 这不是赛车游戏：我们的车子既可二段跳，也可在建筑物上冲刺弹起。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 好友及全球排行榜，登榜者也能正式名列世界各大速通网站。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 没错，我们将前作《浣熊硬探》中阴郁的像素美术世界彻底扭转，摇身一变明亮欢快的赛车游戏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 鼓和贝斯配合而成的碎核（breakcore）原声曲目，首首让人摇头晃脑欲罢不能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > “不会在开车时飞出去的优质方向盘。”</p></li></ul>",
